column10:
Hands down one of my favourite games ever. A beautifully executed Diner-style resource management game.
You get to meet so many of the Touhou girls with all their cuteness and personality. There's so many dishes and the cooking mechanic is so simple but so elegantly done.
I'm so thankful for the English translations. Otherwise I wouldn't have been able to fall in love with this game as much as I have. ;-;

This game is so cute and wholesome, this game is so under priced. It's such a cozy feeling game and it makes me wanna just go lay in bed and play this, the art style is also really pretty! I thought this game would be more barebones too, but every couple minutes it introduces something new also which is crazy of them to do! I know triple A games that don't have this much content. ^^;
Please if you have the money on your steam account, just get it now, don't wait for a sale, the dev deserves all of the money they can get from this game. :>
 (For that reason even though I'm only an hour in I bought all of the DLC!)
